# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# EJoLabs Housing Platform — Environment Config
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Database (Postgres) ──────────────────────
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=postgres
DB_NAME=housing_db
DB_SYNC=true          # Set to false in production — use migrations instead

# ── Redis (BullMQ queues) ────────────────────
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379

# ── Authentication ───────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-random-64-char-string-in-production
# NODE_ENV=production  # Uncomment in production — enforces JWT_SECRET

# ── AI (Gemini) ──────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=    # Required for AI search + listing parsing + auto-apply messages
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-1.5-flash

# ── Frontend URL (used in CORS, emails, Stripe redirects) ──
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ── Email (SMTP) — for Diplomat agent ────────
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=your@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-app-password

# ── Stripe (Payments) ───────────────────────
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...

# ── Scraper Config ───────────────────────────
# SCRAPER_CITIES=Berlin,Hamburg,Munich,Frankfurt
# PROXY_URL=                 # Optional: HTTP proxy for scraping
